caption.body: World Civilization by Viola Frey is located in Boarding Area A in the International Terminal. Frey has created a vocabulary of figures and objects that form a personal mythology. For instance, the suited businessman is a symbol of mainstream respectability, often contrasted with bold, vividly dressed women.
